            <li>Do not reuse passwords on multiple sites</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Why Password Security is Important?</h3>
        <p>
        In cyber security, your password is the first line of defense.
        If your password is weak, hackers can easily guess or brute-force it.
        A strong password protects your personal data, bank accounts,
